Muchidzidzo che[[Jekanyika]] ''(Geodesy)'', nyika yakatarwa nemhando mbiri dzemitsetse. Kune mitsetse yakatarwa yakati sambamba ne[[Mutsazanisi]] inonzi lattitude; kune mitsetse yakatarwa ichibata kuNorth pole neSouth pole inonzi longitude. Mitsetse iyi inoshevedzwa nenhamba dzakarongeka. Nhamba dzemitsetse ye[[lattitude]] dzinoveregwa dzichibva paMutsazanisi dzichienda kumavirira nekumadokero. Nhamba dzemitsetse ye[[longitude]] dzinoverengwa dzichibva pamutsetse weGreenwich Meridian zvichienda kuNorth pole neSouth pole. Greenwich Meridian mutsetse welongitude unopfuura pedyo neRoyal Observatory, Greenwich, kuUnited Kingdom. Naizvozvo nzvimbo dzose dziri panyika dzine nhamba inotaura kuti nzvimbo iri papi mudandemutande remitsetse iyoyi. Ruzivo urwu ndirwo rwakashandiswa muhumhizha hwe[[GPS]], [[Geographical Position System]] chinova chombo chinobatsira kutaura kuti tiri papi uye kupa [[rudzivo]] (direction) rwenzvimbo yatinoda kuenda.
